701561f-a.title: Bronx: Overing Street - Tratman Avenue
701561f-a.text:
Overing Street, at and adjoining (frame house and empty let) the
S.E. corner of Tratman Ave. The apartment house under construction is
at the N.E. corner of Benson Street and Westchester Square.
July 9, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
